{"tid":878491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比連登仔水咗去食鋒味漢堡","createTime":"2018-10-27T07:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T08:09:31.000Z","uid":204646,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d279a0ea7796d52a1735a1230183b79a21682b","tid":878491,"uid":204646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱比40幾蚊試吓個鋒味漢堡<br />\n屌，難食過屎<br />\n個包又甜又鹹，又多水份，我食咗半個已經頂唔順冇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁啱隔離有個好瘦嘅阿伯問我個包係咪唔食(應該係想食二手餐)，我見佢咁慘話係啦<br />\n佢咬咗一啖，好大聲講咗句<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「屌你老母咁撚難食嘅」</span></strong>，之後二話不說dum撚咗落垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為連登仔都話好味嘅食物點都有返咁上下質素啦<br />\n仆你個街我宜家先知原來連登仔中意食狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉，我本身都已經係公屋窮撚，比你地水去食鋒味狗糧又少咁40幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母，鋒味漢堡打手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbab8025a572d1d6f6039c5d992efc89b04617a8","tid":878491,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"樓主知道屎係咩野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5c3220b89b86525403e795674b63164087fce4","tid":878491,"uid":204646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbab8025a572d1d6f6039c5d992efc89b04617a8","tid":878491,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"樓主知道屎係咩野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"a9a47de9af5ae4390a301bd520a028f1044e2e61","tid":878491,"uid":127075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"用m記配料整包，你想有幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎黎去去都係個塊漢堡扒"},{"pid":"ccaf7c62f0b24671cb7787792c6a6713c455df17","tid":878491,"uid":204646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9a47de9af5ae4390a301bd520a028f1044e2e61","tid":878491,"uid":127075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"用m記配料整包，你想有幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎黎去去都係個塊漢堡扒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:09:31.000Z","msg":"都啱，高估咗m記同霆鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}